Allows to define and execute scenario in fluent way.

Example usage:

[Scenario]
[Label("Ticket-1")]
public async Task My_scenario()
{
    await Runner.NewScenario()
        .AddSteps( /* ... */ )
        .RunAsync();
}

Example usage with context:

[Scenario]
[Label("Ticket-1")]
public async Task My_scenario()
{
    await Runner.WithContext<MyContext>()
        .NewScenario()
        .AddSteps( /* ... */ )
        .RunAsync();
}
